chickenGPT: Ferdinand the frog 🐸 croaked nightly, "Cheep cheep! 10 PM!💊" Henrietta the chick chirped, "Thanks, Ferdie!" One night, engrossed in birdseed bingo 🪶, Henrietta forgot! Next morning, Ferdinand found her wearing sunglasses indoors 😎. "What's wrong?" he asked. "Too much bingo," she mumbled. "Now EVERYTHING is cheeping loudly!" Ferdinand facepalmed. 🤦‍♂️ "Should've taken your medicine, chickadee!"
